title: At the Diamond
description:
Our story tonight is called At the Diamond and it’s a story about a warm day, stretched out on a blanket under a tree. It’s also about jumping through a sprinkler on soft green grass, a dried flower with blue petals and a home run hit out past center field. 
So get cozy and ready to sleep.

Buy the book:http://hyperurl.co/NothingMuchHappens

Get an autographed copy and other merch here: https://www.nothingmuchhappens.com/nmh-stuff 

Get our ad-free and bonus episodes here: https://nothingmuchhappens.supportingcast.fm
